{"tid":1007513,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【free lunch and free love】吳綺莉爆Seed寸Andi 卓林：佢係想attack我","createTime":"2019-02-03T20:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T02:32:44.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d887fdd59d5bc1d61a86547d6e13d33f5f9130c5","tid":1007513,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T20:48:42.000Z","msg":"吳綺莉的19歲女兒吳卓林，去年11月宣佈與加拿大籍女友Andi結婚，並決定留港定居，返港後的卓林與Andi，曾因租住旺角一間賓館後欠租，要媽媽吳綺莉出手相救，之後卓林和Andi搬回大坑寓所居住，但不出幾天，兩人又被發現拿着一個大行李箱在元朗，當時卓林直認：「唔會搬返屋企喇！」（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2WM74mC）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WM74mC%EF%BC%89&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToG7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=844e236a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2WM74mC）</a><br />\n事隔十多日後，今日吳綺莉突然在社交網絡中貼上多張Andi的性感舊照，然後寫着：「More blessed to give than to receive my dearest, happy new year, wish you all the best. free lunch and free love」，祝福朋友新年快樂之餘，亦似在揶揄Andi。<br />\n翻看吳綺莉貼出Andi的舊照片中，除了有她為網店影的水着相、與男友人影的合照外，更有去年4月和卓林對話的截圖，而從照片看到，當時卓林更傳了「I'm in danger」的訊息給她。<br />\n而吳綺莉的朋友看完帖後，留言讚嘆她的勇氣，不過吳綺莉就似帶暗示回覆說：「沒好好教好孩子，不想朋友們白幫。」吳綺莉亦向傳媒數臭Andi，指她不停向她的朋友借錢，而吳綺莉則以短訊回覆《蘋果》：「只是說事實，不想欠朋友人情。」至於卓琳今日回覆《蘋果》時表示有不開心：「其實我現在都好努力做嘢support自己，佢要無端端cap低一張一張咁load上去都好花時間，佢明明後面都好晦氣，明明係想attack我，所以有少少唔開心。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190203/large/1549204444_f172.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190203%2Flarge%2F1549204444_f172.jpg&h=777b7b1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190203/large/1549204641_6c28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190203%2Flarge%2F1549204641_6c28.jpg&h=dcdaab49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190203/59221059\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190203%2F59221059&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToG7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=baaee6ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190203%2F59221059&h=0678d5f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190203/59221059</a>"},{"pid":"baaf44285fc9be7208a71adde18c1082e6e7839f","tid":1007513,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T20:51:04.000Z","msg":"who?"},{"pid":"8e0927b9d9fa8849f8660c3b58f1c79692ec176b","tid":1007513,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T20:58:17.000Z","msg":"突然諗到：<br />\n將Chicken attack 改為 Pennis attack<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5f87ee01b3163ac024f2520e5d7ce96900e5fd","tid":1007513,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:32:44.000Z","msg":"推"}]}